question: When I see Sansa stans ship S@ns@n it makes my skin crawl. In the show (unlike the books) how creepy Sandor was towards Sansa isn’t clear. I recently saw this post of him telling Arya that he wanted to take Sansa away and he asked her for a song. They completely ignored the fact that he said that he wanted to rape her. I mean come on. How can people just ignore that.
answer: Because they don’t care about Sansa. They’re Sandor stans who want to ship him with the only good looking person he interacts with and they don’t care that that person is a child
